name: We Were Here - Proof of Moment

metadata.name: Hold my Beer, Pepe #1/143
metadata.description:
Hold my beer, Pepe. 

This token is part of the Proof of Moment (POM) series. 

This particular token symbolizes a significant moment in Web3 history when Pepe took over Twitter and the blockchain. We were here; the Pepe Army isn't going anywhere. 

Homage to Matt Furie.
